Package: tradeengine
Type: Package
Title: Backtesting Engine for Quantitative Trading Strategies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("TradingVerse", "Core Team", email = "info@tradingverse.org", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A powerful and flexible backtesting engine for quantitative trading 
    strategies. Supports vectorized and event-driven backtesting across multiple 
    asset classes including equities, cryptocurrencies, futures, and FX. Features 
    realistic transaction cost modeling, position sizing, portfolio management, 
    and walk-forward analysis. Part of the TradingVerse ecosystem.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
